slib_parms=4\
,masses on the left\
,masses on the right\
0,slope\
,color of the objects\
raw,option words: <span class="tt">one</span>, <span class="tt">url</span>, <span class="tt">html</span>, <span class="tt">raw</span>

slib_out=Drawing of a Roberval balance  (+ size of the image when the option word is \
<span class="tt">url</span>).
slib_comment=The first item of the output is: by default, the flydraw code; \
the address of the generated image if the option word is <span class="tt">url</span> ; \
the html code for inserting image is already inserted for the option <span class="tt">html</span>.\
If <span class="tt">one</span> is in the option words, the form of the object is a rectangle of fixed size.